'''Aces Studio'''，是被[[微软|微软]]收购的游戏工作室，制作过许多流行的游戏，如《[[Microsoft_Flight_Simulator|Microsoft Flight Simulator]]》和《[[Combat_Flight_Simulator|Combat Flight Simulator]]》。由于预算削减，王牌工作室于2009年初关闭<ref name="Ref_Three">{{cite web |url=http://games.ign.com/objects/792/792289.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2011-07-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111105000554/http://games.ign.com/objects/792/792289.html |archivedate=2011-11-05 }}</ref>。

2009年10月，Aces Studio的部分成员成立新游戏工作室[[Cascade_Game|Cascade Game]]。<ref name="Ref_One">{{Cite web |url=http://www.flightsimulatornetwork.com/group/flightsimulatornews/forum/topics/breaking-news-aces-studio |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2009-12-03 |archive-date=2009-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091203152226/http://www.flightsimulatornetwork.com/group/flightsimulatornews/forum/topics/breaking-news-aces-studio |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
